  "name": "Morrison COU1 — FDA centrifugal pump hemolysis credibility assessment (NC-1 clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. This is a fully-assessed, complete-profile package covering all 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors. All factors achieve or exceed required levels. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed across five flow-speed operating points. Decision: Accepted.",
