      "rationale": "CFD solver (OpenFOAM v9) operates under ISO 9001:2015 QMS with version-controlled source, automated regression test suite (312 tests), and traceable build records. All simulation scripts and post-processing routines are stored in a Git repository with signed commits. Code review records and release notes are archived.",
