      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 4,
      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison of CFD-predicted NIH against experimental measurements at all five operating points using validation metric E = (sim − exp)/exp. Maximum |E| = 12.8%; mean |E| = 7.3%. Statistical comparison accounts for experimental repeatability (n=5 replicates per point) and simulation UQ intervals. All predictions lie within experimental uncertainty bands.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
