        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Output comparison acceptance criteria — Gradation 4",
        "description": "Quantitative validation metric must be computed at all operating points with explicit accounting for experimental uncertainty. Maximum relative error must not exceed 15% at any operating point. Statistical significance of agreement must be documented."
      }
    },
    {
