      "rationale": "Simulation execution follows a documented simulation plan reviewed by an independent CFD engineer. Boundary condition assignments independently verified against experimental protocol. Post-processing scripts validated against hand calculations for three representative cases. Analyst training records current for OpenFOAM v9.",
