      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 4,
      "rationale": "All model inputs (fluid properties, geometry dimensions, boundary conditions, hemolysis model coefficients) documented with sources and uncertainties. Probability distributions assigned to six uncertain inputs based on experimental characterization. Inputs propagated through model via Monte Carlo UQ (10,000 samples). Input sensitivity ranked via Sobol indices.",
